              "free_text": [
                " COINCIDENCE BETWEEN THE ASSOCIATED",
                " ALPHA PARTICLE FROM THE NEUTRON PRODUCTION AND THE",
                " NEUTRON INDUCED FISSION FRAGMENT. THE ALPHAS ARE",
                " DETECTED IN A 1 MM THICK PLASTIC SCINTILLATOR,",
                " WITH A 8 MICRONS THICK AL ENTRANCE SHIELD TO STOP",
                " DIFFUSED NEUTRONS. THE  DETECTION EFFICIENCY IS 100.",
